CImg.test
small C++ code samples to test the CImg library (C++ template image processing toolkit).
It could be used as a tutorial or draft developing branch.

The following files refers to the corresponding CImg functions:
* option: command line option (i.e. cimg_library::cimg_option(... )
* debug: debug define tests (e.g. -Dcimg_verbosity3 -Dcimg_strict_warnings)
* display: fill an image container and display it (i.e. CImg::display())

